Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.14,sign_0_1_Magical_Sempai,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,100)}Magical Sempai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:05.27,sign_0_1_Magical_Sempai,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H690AD5&\fad(100,1)}Magi{\c&HB1AD1E&}cal Sem{\c&H7A16E2&}pai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:02.04,sign_1764_7_The_Unknown_Senp,title,0000,0000,0000,,Four {\c&HDDCA21&}Balls {\c&H6A00EE&}Sempai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:02.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Four Balls Sempai."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.01,0:01:08.92,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,You never get tired of playing\Nwith yourself, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:12.05,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't it work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:14.03,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,Could I see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:19.52,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,At last, you show interest...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.52,0:01:21.34,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.34,0:01:23.49,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you anything you want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:25.43,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make it sound like\Nyou ever taught me anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:27.93,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this trick is "The Four Balls."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.93,0:01:30.83,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,You stick one ball in between\Neach of your fingers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:33.07,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,which leaves you with four.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:37.34,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,You can increase or de... de...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:39.00,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,decrease the number of balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:40.32,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,There are just as many as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:43.78,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,To make the ball in the right hand disappear,\Nyou use a technique called palming,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:47.17,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,where you pinch it in your palm\Nto make it look like it disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.58,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,But my hands are slick with sweat,\N so it's not working right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.89,0:01:52.23,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I practiced so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:56.29,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,On the way to school, \Nwhen I'm eating, even in the bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:01:58.84,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,If you can do it in the bath,\Nwhy is sweat a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:03.85,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if my hands\Nare just too small to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.69,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you just get some smaller ones\N that fit your hands better?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:09.93,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the bigger ones looked cooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.93,0:02:11.26,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,Self-defeating vanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:13.73,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,I envy your big hands, Assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:16.63,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,See? They're so much bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:20.49,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing better for doing\Nmagic than big hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:25.62,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,Well... it would look strange\Nif yours were this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:29.80,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,I think they're fine... just the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:33.23,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:36.80,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for touching!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:38.80,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:41.03,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,The sweat! The sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:44.05,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,But he was just complimenting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:46.06,sign_1764_7_The_Unknown_Senp,title,0000,0000,0000,,Ventriloquism {\c&HDDCA21&}Sempai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ventriloquism Sempai."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:48.43,italics,ass,0000,0000,0000,,When I arrived in the club room...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:50.72,italics,ass,0000,0000,0000,,I found Saki-san dead on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:53.20,italics,ass,0000,0000,0000,,What a twist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.60,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:56.48,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:58.44,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:01.35,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,My Ma-kun meter's all petered out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:03.70,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of stupid scale is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:06.95,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You're not with\NMasashi today, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:08.47,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:12.38,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, I was rummaging through\NMa-kun's trash like usual, when...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:16.05,flashback,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Smells like Ma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:22.52,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,And now he hasn't talked to me all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:24.93,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,It's entirely your fault.\NI refuse to comfort you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:28.17,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I know what to do at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:29.07,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.76,0:03:32.44,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,You' aweshome, 'ig Shish! You're sho hrehhy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:35.06,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,You can't flatter me with the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:39.07,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,So you do ventriloquism\Nwith that Masashi puppet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:41.33,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a hobby, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:45.10,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,You open your mouth a tiny bit,\Nthen without moving your lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:46.24,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,I' 'ashashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.84,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,It must be hard to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:51.00,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Bs and Ps are hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:52.65,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,So are Ms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:54.88,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Because you use your lips for those.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:58.56,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,If you can say "pushy," it means\Nyou're on the right track.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:00.76,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,'Ushy. 'Ushy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:02.76,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,See? Hard, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.79,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Puhhy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:06.84,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think I can do it. Puh—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:09.78,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,I get it already! You can stop saying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:13.20,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now you try it, Assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.59,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Use what I taught you,\Nand you'll have it in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:20.17,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Masashi, introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:21.54,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,Nasashi here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:23.78,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,Ny havori'e dri'k ish curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:27.37,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Ma-kun would never say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.03,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,That's the issue? Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:33.42,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel so lonely without Ma-kun around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.97,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,The puppet can't fill the gap in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:36.54,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed to enjoy it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.00,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:41.30,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to mess around with \N{\i1}you{\i0} today, Assistant-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:43.48,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,What? Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.66,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,This is very abrupt, Saki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.58,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hang on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:53.80,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,Saki-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:59.61,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:05.74,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you this Magic Doll\Nas thanks for cheering me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:08.35,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,It's a present from me to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:09.76,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:11.62,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, gotta get to the part-time job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.62,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,You're just going to leave it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.16,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.31,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,White, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.31,sign_1764_7_The_Unknown_Senp,title,0000,0000,0000,,Tailing {\c&HDDCA21&}Sempai
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:35.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tailing Sempai."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.69,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,Now, behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.88,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,It's leaking out! It's totally leaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:40.87,main,ma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.74,main,ma,0000,0000,0000,,Does Sempai have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:47.90,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... you're planning\N on {\i1}that{\i0}, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:49.28,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.08,main,ma,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that. I saw her yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.83,main,ma,0000,0000,0000,,She was walking around with a strange man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:57.19,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.08,sign_8567_107_After_Club,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(108,1)}After Club
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:04.38,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's begin tailing her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:05.58,main,ma,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who the man is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:08.96,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he just accosted her\Nfor a survey or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.22,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,She entered a family restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:13.03,main,ma,0000,0000,0000,,Behavioral psychology\Nsuggests it's suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:15.97,main,ma,0000,0000,0000,,for a teenage female to enter\Na family restaurant alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:17.85,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,You're so smart, Ma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:19.63,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Did you use that mental stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:21.48,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about being a mentalist?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:25.11,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Two plates of cake and two glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:28.11,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,And she's sitting in the back,\Nwary of eyes upon her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.11,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,She's clearly waiting for someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:33.12,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,She drank one down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:40.18,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,She's practicing the coin trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:42.17,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:47.08,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,She ended up eating both\Nslices of cake by herself, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:48.42,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,I think you were off base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.43,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,She's watching her smartphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.10,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,She took off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.31,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,She probably needs to hit the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.94,main,ma,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's meeting someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:06:59.84,main,ma,0000,0000,0000,,When one puts their face that\Nclose to their smartphone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:02.73,main,ma,0000,0000,0000,,it's proof that they're engaging\Nin intimate messaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.21,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,Are you enjoying this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:06.32,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,She's running right for the convenience store!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.07,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,She must be going for...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:10.23,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,The bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:14.32,sign_10366_135_Missing_Missing_,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(270,140,270,220)}Thank you for \Nalways keeping \Nthe bathroom {\c&HB3A7E4&\3c&HFBF7FF&}clean
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:14.32,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,She's been in there a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:18.89,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,But if I'm in the toilet, I'll be\Nfixing my hair and my make-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:21.84,main,ma,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! That explains\Nwhy she's been in there so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:23.21,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's time to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:25.20,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,She's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:28.95,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,She looks cleaned out, is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.41,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,We tailed her for half the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:35.60,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,and not only did she not meet anyone,\Nall she did was eat and poop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:39.44,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, there's no\N way Sempai has a boy—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:41.45,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Were you waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.51,main,sem,0000,0000,0000,,I got a little sidetracked,\Nso I'm running late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:47.36,main,mimu,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I didn't wait long at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:49.22,top,mimu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:50.32,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:50.32,top,sem,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:52.36,main,ma,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:56.04,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Assistant-kun, do you like\NMagic Girl that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:58.08,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll console you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.93,main,saki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about as big as she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:01.07,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:03.25,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm trying to be her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.86,main,ass,0000,0000,0000,,It's like when you take care of a stray cat,
